context: <user> I'm looking for an indonesian restaurant that's moderate in price. <system> There are no Indonesian restaurants in the moderate price range would you like me to search for something else? <user> Are you sure? I thought there was one located in the centre of town. <system> Unfortunately I do not see any indonesian restaurants. Maybe you would like asain instead? <user> Asian oriental food sounds good. What options do you have available? <system> I have a few, what price range do you prefer? <user> Im not really worried about price. Which do you suggest that is located in the centre? <system> Th Kymmoy is expensive but very nice.<user> I think I would like to be in the moderate price range please. <system> The yippee noddle bar is in the moderate price range. Would you like to book a table?<user> Actually, can you give me the phone number for Yippee Noodle Bar instead? <system> Absolutely. Their phone number is 01223518111. Is there anything else I can help you with?<user> I am also looking for a train. The train should arrive by 16:15 and should leave on Friday. <system> I'm sure we can find your perfect train for you. What are your departure and arrival locations?<user> I want to go to norwich from cambridge. <system> The first train from Cambridge to Norwich leaves at 05:36, and there are trains every hour thereafter. The duration of the trip is 79 minutes. Which departure time works best for you?<user> Can you suggest one? I would like to arrive in Norwich about 4:15 PM. <system> I would recommend TR8314, which will get you there at 15:55. Would you like me to book your ticket?<user> Yes, one ticket please. <system> Booking was successful, the total fee is 17.6 GBP payable at the station .<user> When does the TR8314 leave? <system>
